item.title: Building a single page application with Elm
item.description: Hi there, its been a very long while since I last blogged, I promised this ages ago, its a partial sample chapter for a book I was planning on Elm but the publisher started to muck me about so it never happened. I also have the table of contents for the rest of the book but I guess your not interested in a book Im not writing so I have omitted that.
